From: Ian Rogers <irogers@google.com>
Date: Mon, 18 Nov 2024 14:53:40 -0800
Subject: tool api fs: Correctly encode errno for read/write open failures
Git-commit: 05be17eed774aaf56f6b1e12714325ca3a266c04
Patch-mainline: v6.14-rc1
References: perf-sle16.1-v6.19-userspace-update

Switch from returning -1 to -errno so that callers can determine types
of failure.

